                        <th>Goat's Word</th>
                        <th>Tech Word</th>
                        <th>Human Meaning</th>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Project Folder</td>
                        <td><strong>Repository</strong></td>
                        <td>The cloud folder tracking every change.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Suggestion Box</td>
                        <td><strong>Issue</strong></td>
                        <td>A chat thread about a problem.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Proposal</td>
                        <td><strong>Pull Request</strong></td>
                        <td>Asking to merge your edits into the main book.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Personal Copy</td>
                        <td><strong>Fork</strong></td>
                        <td>A copy you can mess up without breaking the real one.</td>
